OL,5,G2100 Bangers & Cash
OL,6,     FHonda NSX/Range Rover: Dave is
OL,7,     F'lost in France' en route to
OL,8,     Fpicking up a rare Honda NSX. Derek
OL,9,     Fheads to a toy factory where some
OL,10,     Fvintage motorbikes are stashed.
OL,11,G2200 Train Truckers
OL,12,     FRoyal Highland Fusilier: The Royal
OL,13,     FHighland Fusilier, a 100-ton
OL,14,     FDeltic diesel engine, must be
OL,15,     Fhauled from Leicestershire to
OL,16,     FWirksworth in Cheshire.
